# GSNR Project

## 📌 Overview
GSNR is a software project developed to provide an efficient and user-friendly solution for managing and processing system operations. The project focuses on simplicity, performance, and scalability while delivering a smooth user experience.

---

## 🚀 Features
- User-friendly interface
- Fast and efficient performance
- Secure data handling
- Easy navigation
- Scalable architecture
- Database integration support
- Responsive design

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Java / Kotlin
- Android Studio
- Firebase
- Room Database
- XML
- Git & GitHub

