## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/sadanandabiradar1-stack/GSNR.git
```

### Open in Android Studio
1. Open Android Studio
2. Click on **Open Project**
3. Select the cloned repository
4. Sync Gradle files
5. Run the project

